description: Scanning the rural countryside, you are likely to see many wonders of nature, but none so striking in this landscape as the picturesque physique of Zack Lemec. Perched on a boulder underneath the bright sun, he smolders and shimmers as the light glistens off his sun drenched body. Stripping naked to soak in the rays, he basks in the warmth and fondles himself by a deep blue pond. Working himself into a frenzy, he sits back against rock and reclines amidst the foliage, natural as can be, and without a care in the world. The good life, he thinks, as he explodes forth in a gooey offering to the day... the good life indeed.Enjoy!
title: Zack Lemec
